N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 333.4 - Enrollment blank

State Regulations

An enrollment blank in the form prescribed by section 174
or subdivision 1 of section 369 of the Election Law shall be enclosed and
mailed or delivered to the military voter in the envelope containing the
military ballot. Notes
